** data **
classifier: data/classifier/classifier.pkl
  -> built @ classifier.save
encoder: data/encoder/encoder.hdf5[/layer_<i> & /n_layers] && data/encoder/decoder.hdf5[<same>]
  -> built @ encoder-trainer.save
raw csv: data/db/questions.csv
raw text questions: data/db/questions.txt
  -> built @ import
raw text questions for pre-train : data/db/subtitles.txt
classes: data/db/classes.hdf5[/data]
  -> built @ import
encoded questions: data/db/encoded_questions.hdf5[/data]
  -> built @ encoder.load & import

** be careful **
when importing don't save or load components (import component not linked to controller => no state control)

